Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left everything\Nthis world's got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we were able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that you'd come, Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I think about it,\Nyou've always protected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you're our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...you guys sure did pull one\Noutrageous stunt back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, to think that you shot\Nthrough the World Government's flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All we did was take back a friend\Nwho was taken away from us.
