Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, hey, hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, this isn't good. Without thinking, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'm gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know where Usopp is,\NSogeking? I can't find him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry. He went back\Nahead of us on a small boat earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this ship actually belongs to him now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is it they need\Nin order to recognize Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As we suspected, I can't find\Nanyone anywhere on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who on earth sailed this ship to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But we definitely heard\Nthat voice calling out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, someone most certainly called to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said all this time...\Nit was the Merry's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Merry?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. There's no way a ship would talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda felt that way too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way something\Nlike that... could happen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was a mystery to us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...for some reason, these words\Nremained in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if this person actually\Nsaid it or I was imagining things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry you guys for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This may sound stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...I feel that it might've been\Nan incarnation of the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm crazy, don't you?\NYou don't have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This person looked like a sailor\Nholding a wooden hammer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw a Klabautermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Klabau...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Klabautermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the legends known among sailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The more care the ship receives,\Nthe more it appreciates the sailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship probably wanted to somehow\Ncarry you across to the other shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was able to encounter a crew\Nthat she wanted to carry so badly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that she'd borrow a human form to appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's been very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...who talked to me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...was really you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a ship coming towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Galley-La Company's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They rushed out in Aqua Laguna and\Nstill made it okay! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They came back from Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahoy! Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid-berg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crazy lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They took on the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they really took everything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Their ship is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?!\NWhat happened all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden? Isn't this just natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was declared that Merry could no longer sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Merry is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! This is bad! Merry is in trouble!\NPlease do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... This is good timing!\NYou guys're all shipwrights, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you! Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our friend who has been\Ntraveling with us all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And just a bit ago she saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already done everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone on the scrap heap island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this... the Straw Hats' ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage must've been caused by\NAqua Laguna. It's in a terrible state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's beyond just damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to set sail one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no hope left for this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?!\NAnother big wave is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You want to set sail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is still stormy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go alone if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you go out there all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching a miracle right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A miracle of a ship that\Nhas long passed its limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a shipwright for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never seen a pirate ship this incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lived a splendid life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the seas of adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... are you guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry... The seabed is dark and lonesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll watch you to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was good that Usopp wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way... that he could bear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone must someday say farewell.\NThis is a man's parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a single tear should be shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He, too... is prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for carrying us\Nfor such a long time, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A caravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:17:01.04,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Every day we'd play covered in mud until the sun set
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Going Merry pirate ship is all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:10.59,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,It's hard to abandon those innocent days we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to our new ship and crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:20.48,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm a dreamer, I'm still me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! The Merry\Ngot damaged quite a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When navigating a sailboat,\Neveryone has to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:29.44,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,So things don't all have to fit together like a jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn it appropriately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--Aw...\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannon practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:39.20,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Just as someone's "Yes" could be a "No" to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure don't fly good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! You hit it on your first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:47.75,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,you'll surely always be free
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...! I really hit it on my first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:58.89,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Even if tomorrow a wind passes through and breaks the puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:06.73,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,No one would blame you for that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Hey! That's my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance to the Grand Line\Nlies ahead of that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:13.24,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.95,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become a master swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to draw a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:27.21,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In order... to become a\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going... to the Grand Line!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:36.68,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,We know the pain that you hold in your heart, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:46.90,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,If you ever depart this ship and live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance to the Grand Line is a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:56.24,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest sea in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! We're flying out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look back! We're going straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me... join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for me to go or go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me stay on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... Then I guess\Nwe have no choice... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:02.93,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,We continue to dream even today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this ship's navigator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:16.99,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,Carrying the feelings you entrusted with us as well
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! The ship is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:27.62,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,We once again cross these rough seas and fight the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:36.09,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,So that our promise won't become a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:46.93,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,And someday, to you who departed our ship and live in a different world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:57.53,Insert Song ♪,,0,0,0,,we'll deliver the completed puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to carry you even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to continue going on\Nadventures with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's us who have to apologize, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at steering...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I ran you into icebergs at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time I tore the sails, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro and Sanji are stupid,\Nso they broke all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp would fix them each time,\Nbut he isn't good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's us who have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much... for taking\Ngood care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I really have been happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite an ordeal, but we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The restoration of Water Seven starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... There seems to be a ruckus outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma! The Navy is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Peace Interrupted!\NA Navy Vice Admiral with a Fist of Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
